sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>(platform sidecar)
    participant EvalHub as eval-hub API<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant K8sAuth as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>(Auth)
    participant K8sJobs as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>(Batch v1)
    participant MLflow as MLflow Tracking<br/>5000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant PostgreSQL as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP

    Note over User,PostgreSQL: Flow 1: Evaluation Job Creation

    User->>KRBAC: POST /api/v1/evaluations/jobs<br/>Bearer Token (K8s SA)
    KRBAC->>EvalHub: Forward (authenticated)
    EvalHub->>K8sAuth: TokenReview<br/>TLS 1.2+ / In-cluster SA token
    K8sAuth-->>EvalHub: Identity (user, groups)
    EvalHub->>K8sAuth: SubjectAccessReview<br/>trustyai.opendatahub.io/evaluations:create<br/>Namespace: X-Tenant header
    K8sAuth-->>EvalHub: Allowed
    EvalHub->>MLflow: Create Experiment<br/>Bearer Token
    MLflow-->>EvalHub: Experiment ID
    EvalHub->>PostgreSQL: Persist Job Record
    PostgreSQL-->>EvalHub: OK
    EvalHub->>K8sJobs: Create ConfigMap (job spec + sidecar config)<br/>TLS 1.2+ / SA token
    K8sJobs-->>EvalHub: ConfigMap created
    EvalHub->>K8sJobs: Create Job (3-container pod)<br/>TLS 1.2+ / SA token
    K8sJobs-->>EvalHub: Job created
    EvalHub-->>User: 201 Created (Job ID)

    Note over User,PostgreSQL: Flow 2: Evaluation Job Execution (in-pod)

    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Init as eval-runtime-init
    participant Adapter as Eval Adapter<br/>(lm-eval / LightEval / etc.)
    participant Sidecar as eval-runtime-sidecar<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (localhost)
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Init->>S3: Download test data<br/>TLS 1.2+ / AWS IAM credentials
    S3-->>Init: Test data objects
    Note over Init: Init container completes

    Adapter->>Sidecar: POST /api/v1/evaluations/jobs/{id}/events<br/>localhost:8080 (no auth)
    Sidecar->>EvalHub: Forward status event<br/>HTTPS / Bearer SA token
    EvalHub-->>Sidecar: ACK

    Adapter->>Sidecar: POST /api/2.0/mlflow/runs/log-metric<br/>localhost:8080 (no auth)
    Sidecar->>MLflow: Forward to MLflow<br/>HTTPS / Bearer token
    MLflow-->>Sidecar: OK

    Adapter->>Sidecar: PUT /{oci-repo}/blobs<br/>localhost:8080 (no auth)
    Sidecar->>OCI: Push artifacts<br/>TLS 1.2+ / Bearer (challenge/response)
    OCI-->>Sidecar: OK

    Adapter->>Sidecar: Final status: completed
    Sidecar->>EvalHub: POST /events (completed)<br/>HTTPS / Bearer SA token
    EvalHub->>MLflow: Tag run with results
    EvalHub->>PostgreSQL: Update job status
